# OmniRadon workspace — environment example
#
# This workspace repo does not have its own runtime environment.
# Each service manages its own .env file inside its own directory.
#
# Relevant .env files per service:
#   gateway/.env          ← copy from gateway/.env.example
#   auth-service/.env     ← copy from auth-service/.env.example
#
# shell and diary do not require manual .env setup for local development.
